Titolo: Light the Flower

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Light the Flower is a puzzle game for iOS developed by Finnish studio Tribeflame and published by Chillingo. The game can be bought from App Store (iOS) for $0,99. It was released on March 22, 2012 and had its latest update on September 27, 2012. The game has received mostly positive reviews and has a Metacritic score of 80.

